tigious Californian university named after  Senator Leland Stanford , on whose land it was built. It may also in some cases have been adopted as an alternative elaboration of   Stan ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705187,"age":1,"year":"1215","julianDay":2164830,"title":"Magna Carta","description":"King John of England agreed to a charter of rights called the Magna Carta. The document was originally drafted by the Archbishop of Canterbury to establish peace between King John and a group of rebel barons. The Magna Carta was completed in 1215 and is now considered to be one of the greatest constitutional documents of all time.","url":"https://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk/education/medieval/magna-carta/","urlTitle":"National Archives - Magna Carta","jurisdictionLevel":0},{"id":1705188,"age":10,"year":"1224","julianDay":2168117,"title":"France Declares War on England","description":"France declared war on England as Louis VIII of France attacked Poitou and northern Gascony.","jurisdictionLevel":0}],"lifeSummary":"Lucy of Stanford was born before 1214, in England. She married William d'Wasseburne before 1234, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died after July 1255, in Stanford on Teme, Worcestershire, England."},"et":{"before 1214–after July 1255":"enne 1214–pärast juulit 1255","1214–1255":"1214–1255","1234–1299":"1234–1299","before June 1255":"enne juunit 1255","1215":"1215","before 1214":"enne 1214","1214":"1214","1224":"1224","before 1234":"enne 1234","1234":"1234","after July 1255":"pärast juulit 1255","1299":"1299","1255":"1255","Bef July 1234":"enne juulit 1234","Stanford-on-Teme, Worcestershire, England":"Stanford on Teme, Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Stanford on Teme, Worcestershire, England":"Stanford on Teme, Worcestershire, England","Knights Wasseburne, Worcestershire, England":"Worcestershire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"before 1214–after July 1255":"ennen vuotta 1214–heinäkuu 1255 jä